WISH LIST TASKS:
1) Improve plugin architecture so that it is possible to have plugin specific options in config dialog. This would likely mean reworking all the filter stuff.
2) Threading, allowing reading (click) when checking new mail (big job).

------------------------------
***TO ADD NEW LANG***
use msginit -l <lang> in po dir to create po file
translate the po file
add the lang to ALL_LINGUAS in configure.ac
aclocal;autoconf;automake
./configure;make etc
